---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experience | Joydip Dutta">
  <section class="animate-in fade-in slide-in-from-bottom-4 mb-24 max-w-2xl duration-700 ease-out">
    <h1 class="text-foreground mb-4 text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter md:text-5xl">
      Experience_Log
    </h1>
    <p class="text-muted inline-block rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-950 p-4 font-mono">
      <span class="text-accent">~ $ grep "Software Development Engineer" system.log</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="relative ml-3 border-l border-zinc-800 pb-12 md:ml-4">
    <!-- Timeline Item 1 -->
    <div class="relative mb-16 pl-8 md:pl-10">
      <span
        class="bg-accent ring-background absolute top-1.5 -left-1.25 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full ring-4"
      ></span>

      <div class="mb-2 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between">
        <h3 class="text-foreground text-xl font-bold">Software Development Engineer</h3>
        <span
          class="text-accent bg-accent/10 border-accent/20 mt-2 inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs font-medium md:mt-0"
          >Jan 2026 – Present</span
        >
      </div>

      <h4 class="text-accent mb-5 flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm">
        @ Gunpowder Innovations
        <span class="text-zinc-600">| London, UK - Remote</span>
      </h4>

      <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {
          ["61 Prisma Models", "31 Event Types", "AES-256-GCM"].map((metric) => (
            <span class="rounded-md border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/80 px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-300">
              {metric}
            </span>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <ul class="max-w-2xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono">»</span>
          <span
            >Architected <strong class="text-zinc-200">Row-Level Security (ACL)</strong> across the entire
            multi-tenant platform with Redis-backed caching for strict data isolation.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono">»</span>
          <span
            >Integrated WealthKernel & Plaid APIs with an event-driven <strong class="text-zinc-200"
              >BullMQ webhook pipeline</strong
            > and secure signature verification.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-accent mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono">»</span>
          <span
            >Implemented <strong class="text-zinc-200">field-level encryption</strong> with zero-downtime
            key rotation for financial compliance at low query latency.</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline Item 2 -->
    <div class="relative mb-16 pl-8 md:pl-10">
      <span
        class="ring-background absolute top-1.5 -left-1.25 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-600 ring-4"
      ></span>

      <div class="mb-2 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between">
        <h3 class="text-foreground text-xl font-bold">Software Development Engineer</h3>
        <span
          class="mt-2 inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 px-2.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500 md:mt-0"
          >Jan 2023 – Dec 2025</span
        >
      </div>

      <h4 class="mb-5 flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm text-zinc-400">
        @ The Internet Folks
        <span class="text-zinc-600">| Bhopal, MP - Remote</span>
      </h4>

      <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {
          ["30k+ Users", "TypeScript + Go", "Multi-LLM (BYOK)", "5 Products"].map((metric) => (
            <span class="rounded-md border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/80 px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-300">
              {metric}
            </span>
          ))
        }
      </div>

      <ul class="max-w-2xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            >Maintained backend services for <strong class="text-zinc-200">30,000+ users</strong> with
            dynamic MongoDB partitioning for millions of records.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            >Built <strong class="text-zinc-200">polyglot microservices</strong> routing tracking data
            to ClickHouse and relational data to PostgreSQL.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            >Developed hybrid AI with <strong class="text-zinc-200">pgvector semantic search</strong
            > and multi-LLM generation with BYOK support.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            >Created multi-tenant <strong class="text-zinc-200">"Fund as a Service"</strong> platform
            with strict financial ledger tracking.</span
          >
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            >Built <strong class="text-zinc-200">AgriEasy</strong> digital agriculture platform with real-time
            negotiation and automated crop care schedules.</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline Item 3 -->
    <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-10">
      <span
        class="ring-background absolute top-1.5 -left-1.25 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-zinc-600 ring-4"
      ></span>

      <div class="mb-2 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between">
        <h3 class="text-foreground text-xl font-bold">Software Development Intern</h3>
        <span
          class="mt-2 inline-flex w-fit items-center rounded-full border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 px-2.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-500 md:mt-0"
          >June 2022 – Aug 2022</span
        >
      </div>

      <h4 class="mb-5 flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-sm text-zinc-400">
        @ AUM Capital Market Private Limited
        <span class="text-zinc-600">| Kolkata, WB</span>
      </h4>

      <div class="mb-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span
          class="rounded-md border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/80 px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-300"
          >80% Less Manual Work</span
        >
      </div>

      <ul class="max-w-2xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-400">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="mt-0.5 mr-3 font-mono text-zinc-600">»</span>
          <span
            >Automated <strong class="text-zinc-200">government bond calculations</strong> and payment
            reminders with React and Node.js.</span
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
